==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: optimum
<hw>optimum</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Best possible or most desirable;
-- usually under a restriction expressed or implied; <as>as, an
<ex>optimum</ex> return on capital; <ex>optimum</ex> concentration of a
drug; an <ex>optimum</ex> result</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> optimal.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>optimum</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: optimum
<hw>optimum</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The most favorable condition,
greatest degree, or largest amount possible under given
circumstances.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Option</ent>⟦br⟧
